Jacques Castelot https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jacques_Castelot 0 Jacques Castelot (11 July 1914 – 25 August 1989) was a French film actor. He appeared in 86 films between 1938 and 1982. His brother was the writer André Castelot and their father was the Symbolist painter Maurice Chabas. Jacques_Castelot ( 11_July_1914 – 25_August_1989 ) was a_French_film_actor .
